paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the structural analysis of ATTRwt amyloid fibrils using cryo-EM, focusing on the structural homogeneity of fibrils in patients with ATTRwt amyloidosis. No specific genetic variants in the TTR gene are mentioned.

challenges: The paper did not mention any specific genetic variants in the TTR gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on structural analysis and did not provide genetic variant data for the TTR gene.
